Two-pane split container wrapping views::ResizeArea. Replaces the
BoxLayoutView that held tasklist+browserchrome so users can drag the
vertical divider, snap at 0/50/100% on release, and nudge with Alt+Left /
Alt+Right. Generalizes to vertical-orientation splits for future phases
(terminal ↔ editor, etc.).
